(deflayer navigation
  esc      f1     f2   f3       f4   f5   f6   f7   f8   f9    f10  f11  f12        prnt slck brk
  grv      1      2    3        4    5    6    7    8    9     0    -    =    bspc  mlft @mu mrgt
  tab      home   up   end      pgup t    y    u    i    o     p    [    ]    \     @ml  @md @mr
  lctl     left   down right    pgdn g    left down up   right ;    '    lrld
  lsft     C-left x    C-right  v    b    n    m    ,    .     /    rsft
  lctl     lmet lalt           spc                    ralt menu rctl
)
